title: FANTOM Update: Raise Collateral Cap of $ETH, $YFI, $SUSHI
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral cap on C.R.E.A.M. FANTOM market for the following assets: ETH, YFI, SUSHI.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Tokens are currently capped out on Fantom and this will improve the market.

For:

Raise Collateral Cap-
$ETH to 671 / $2,200,000 USD
$YFI to 18 / $600,000 USD
$SUSHI to 53,860 / $600,000 USD

Against:
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
